Package: bwcopyeditor
Type: Package
Title: Bellwether Copyeditor - LLM-Powered Copyediting Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A tool that uses LLM models to copyedit PDF documents according
    to project context and Bellwether style conventions. Supports text
    extraction for publications and image conversion for slide decks.
    Preserves page numbers and returns structured output that can be
    coerced to a table or CSV.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    pdftools,
    stringr,
    glue,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
